#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/contribute.en.xhtml:18
msgid ""
"We are a diverse community of people from all over Europe and beyond, who "
"are committed to <a href=\"/freesoftware/freesoftware.html\">Free Software</"
"a>. If you feel likewise, <strong>join us in our work for freedom</strong>. "
"There are many ways to engage and you will surely find a way that fits your "
"interests and skills."
msgstr ""

