#. type: Content of: <html><body><h1>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:12
#: fsfe.org/contribute/spreadtheword.en.xhtml:14
msgid "Spread the word!"
msgstr ""

#. type: Attribute 'alt' of: <html><body><div><div><img>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:18
msgid "megaphone"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:21
msgid ""
"You found your way here, because - like us - you care about Free Software "
"and digital civil rights. We need your help to spread the word about the "
"advantages of Free Software, and to explain others why they should care "
"about Freedom, too. Advocating for Free Software is fun and arguably one of "
"the best ways to help the Free Software movement! On this page you find "
"graphics to use and leaflets to be printed by yourself to support and help "
"you in spreading the word. We have a separate page if you search for <a "
"href=\"spreadtheword.html\">professionally printed promotion material by the "
"FSFE</a>, available for no cost."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h2>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:27
msgid "Graphics to use"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:31
msgid "On this page you find"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><ul><li>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:33
msgid "<a href=\"#graphics\">Graphics to use</a>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><ul><li>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:34
msgid "<a href=\"#political-leaflets\">Printable information material</a>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><div><ul><li>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:35
msgid "<a href=\"#promo-material\">Order FSFE's Promotion Material</a>"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><p>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:39
msgid ""
"All graphics you find on this page can be used to promote Free Software in "
"general and the work of FSFE in particular. Feel free to copy, spread and "
"use them as long as you avoid the appearance that - whatever you use it for "
"- is an official product or the official opinion of the FSFE. Thank you very "
"much for promoting Freedom!"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <html><body><h3>
#: fsfe.org/contribute/getyourgraphic.en.xhtml:41
msgid "Logo of the Free Software Foundation Europe"
msgstr ""

